WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.309
A new client brings documents, data,

2
00:00:03.309 --> 00:00:07.282
people and decisions that often remain in separate files.

3
00:00:07.282 --> 00:00:10.627
Vera carries them through one connected journey.

4
00:00:14.323 --> 00:00:18.350
It starts with the incoming folder, builds the inventory,

5
00:00:18.350 --> 00:00:23.013
gathers readable data and turns open points into precise requests.

6
00:00:26.709 --> 00:00:32.094
It then uses that same evidence to structure identity data, executors,

7
00:00:32.094 --> 00:00:35.863
beneficial owners, services and engagement terms.

8
00:00:39.559 --> 00:00:41.332
The plans for engagement,

9
00:00:41.332 --> 00:00:46.437
privacy and AI information share that basis with a draft AML assessment.

10
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:54.358
Actions, dates and reviews help keep the working file current.

11
00:00:54.358 --> 00:00:56.812
The firm can see what is documented,

12
00:00:56.812 --> 00:01:00.424
what remains open and what needs professional review.

13
00:01:04.119 --> 00:01:09.200
From the first folder to a working client file that can be updated over time.
